These are Puzzles for 7x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-1::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: july, april, february
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, baccarat, aristoff
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: azalea, dahlia, iris
There are 3 different favourite colors: light-blue, ivory, apricot
House: wooden, art-deco, tower
There are 3 different nationalities: colombian, german, italian
3 different pets are kept: hamster, bird, cat
 1. the owner of the hamster is the german##1
 2. the owner of the cat is the person who likes apricot##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in february is between the italian and the person who's birthday is in april##2
 4. the art-deco house is on the left of the colombian##1
 5. the person who likes ivory is the aristoff-smoker##1
 6. the person who growsiris is the colombian##1
 7. the person who growsiris is on the left of the tiparillo-smoker##1
 8. the owner of the bird is on the left of the wooden house##1
 9. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the person who likes ivory##1
10. the person who growsdahlia is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |
| Birthday      | april    | february   | july           |
| Cigar          | baccarat       | aristoff    | tiparillo         |
| Flower         | dahlia    | iris  | azalea        |
| Color           | light-blue | ivory   | apricot      |
| House   | art-deco        | tower    | wooden       |
| Nationality   | german     | colombian  | italian       |
| Pet         | hamster     | bird | cat |

