The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: daffodil, iris, zinnia
3 different games are played: backgammon, go, billiard
The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, jet-ski, car
City: prague, miami, liverpool
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: may, october, march
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: baseball, water-polo, weightlifting
 1. the person who's birthday is in march is the person traveling to miami##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in march is the person playing billiard##1
 3. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
 4. the person who's sport is baseball is between the analyst and the software-developer##2
 5. the person traveling to liverpool is on the far left##1
 6. the analyst is the person driving the bus##1
 7. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 8. the person who growsdaffodil is the person playing backgammon##1
 9. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person driving the car##1
10. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |       3       |
| Job      | software-developer   | fisherman    | analyst         |
| Flower          | daffodil    | iris | zinnia          |
| Game   | backgammon  | billiard  | go     |
| Transport   | car       | jet-ski      | bus         |
| City   | liverpool      | miami   | prague    |
| Birthday           | may        | march      | october         |
| Sport         | water-polo | baseball  | weightlifting |

