The people have 3 different jobs:  chef, musician, software-developer
City: liverpool, boston, london
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: rose, dahlia, zinnia
 1. the person eating kale is the person traveling to boston##1
 2. the software-developer is the person who likes lilac##1
 3. the palace house is the person eating peas##1
 4. the tower house is the person traveling to boston##1
 5. the person who growsdahlia is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1
 6. the tower house is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1
 7. the person who likes ebony is between the musician and the person who's birthday is in september##2
 8. the musician is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
 9. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
10. the person traveling to london is on the right of the person eating kale##1
11. the musician is the person eating peas##1

.:: Answer ::.
