The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, daffodil, bellflower
3 different games are played: go, whist, mah-jongg
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, old-henry, bolivar
 1. the old-henry-smoker is on the right of the person who likes lavender##1
 2. the person who likes chestnut is the person playing mah-jongg##1
 3. the bolivar-smoker is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
 4. the person who growsdaffodil is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
 5. the person who growsballoon-flower is between the person driving the airplane and the person who likes chestnut##2
 6. the person who likes lavender is on the right of the palace house##1
 7. the person who growsballoon-flower is the farmhouse house##1
 8. the musician is the bolivar-smoker##1
 9. the person who likes lavender is between the musician and the social-worker##2
10. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the person playing whist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2        |       3       |
| Color      | chestnut | lavender           | turquise      |
| House         | palace       | farmhouse         | futuristic       |
| Job           | musician    | security-guard | social-worker |
