 2. the colonial house is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
 3. the person traveling to liverpool is the person playing canasta##1
 4. the person traveling to colone is on the far right##1
 5. the person playing canasta is between the person playing go and the person watching mystery movies##2
 6. the person playing canasta is between the person playing poker and the owner of the snake##2
 7. the colonial house is between the person who growsmarigold and the person traveling to paris##2
 8. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
 9. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
10. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is the person who growsmarigold##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |       2       |     3      |
