The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: lily, rose, dahlia
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: indie, funk, rock
City: marseilles, edinburgh, colone
There 3 different types of food: asparagus, tomato, kiwi
 1. the person traveling to colone is in the middle##1
 2. the ranch-style house is in the middle##1
 3. the person who growsdahlia is on the right of the tiparillo-smoker##1
 4. the bolivar-smoker is the person watching disaster movies##1
 5. the person eating asparagus is on the right of the person who growsdahlia##1
 6. the fan of rock is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
 7. the person eating kiwi is between the art-deco house and the person who growslily##2
 8. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person traveling to marseilles##1
 9. the person watching disaster movies is the person eating asparagus##1
10. the fan of rock is on the left of the fan of funk##1
11. the person eating asparagus is the person who growslily##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |
| House      | art-deco | ranch-style      | wooden      |
| Cigar         | tiparillo     | bongani     | bolivar  |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | adventure  | disaster |
| Flower   | rose  | dahlia     | lily |
| Music-Genre           | indie        | rock | funk     |
| City         | marseilles    | colone | edinburgh   |
| Food     | tomato        | kiwi        | asparagus   |

